rown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買定焦是常識吧</blockquote><br />\n轉會算啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/210009_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F210009_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27c1b825&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f45963996b486e34123ed9a57ac96957251755d0","tid":472642,"uid":8477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"路過想問下 <br />\nM6無左EVF <br />\n日頭會唔會好多時太光搞到睇唔到mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊後備機買M5定M6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dd8d8cd16cc51aec269ae7ac31070044e378bf","tid":472642,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"有無EF mount adapter?<br />\n買支EF 50 F1.8 stm經adapter插落部機度"},{"pid":"e69ebbb201fc07a352adedf2058f33d36aed49e7","tid":472642,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>路過想問下 <br />\nM6無左EVF <br />\n日頭會唔會好多時太光搞到睇唔到mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊後備機買M5定M6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n實會有機會睇唔到, 雖然佢有反mon可以有限地調整角度<br />\n有evf部機就會大舊左重左, 自己取捨"},{"pid":"3a007667e8f5a568c5cda311ec4964236fac89d1","tid":472642,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早排買左EOS M6連EF-M 15-45mm f/3.5-6.3 IS STM<br />\n想換枝可以影人好啲既鏡頭 各位巴打有冇好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買定焦是常識吧</blockquote><br />\n轉會算啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/210009_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F210009_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27c1b825&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n影人Canon有對手？<br />\n我用Nikon 都係咁話"},{"pid":"45e6017060e56e33ad5d25e357106f8f583cd69f","tid":472642,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9b35fd3c407cddc36bf0b652a6ab14b85bc2f21","tid":472642,"uid":62063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:30:56.000Z","msg":"你講下而家有咩唔好/不足先"},{"pid":"ee048be77347107cd9f458c4b6c720d6233a7eab","tid":472642,"uid":48975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:12:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無EF mount adapter?<br />\n買支EF 50 F1.8 stm經adapter插落部機度</blockquote><br />\n就係諗緊買唔買得過 如果買左 之後EOS M出定焦就好似好傻仔"},{"pid":"94541b74b89724d686b5a95f6a5d4f2ced6bff87","tid":472642,"uid":48975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講下而家有咩唔好/不足先</blockquote><br />\n係我太廢 焦距呢件事完全唔識掌握 上網睇過用定焦可以易上手少少 就有少少心動想換過枝"},{"pid":"8994b48c18c9dd7ce2631039a7ca16831edbb334","tid":472642,"uid":26080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T23:59:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>路過想問下 <br />\nM6無左EVF <br />\n日頭會唔會好多時太光搞到睇唔到mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊後備機買M5定M6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真答你，買m5<br />\n貴小小有埋EVF <br />\n重小小，小到好難感覺到<br />\nTouch and drag<br />\n同埋m6 落左外置EVF 就冇得落閃<br />\n向下反mon 自拍果陣，望個mon = 望鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n我之前用緊m3, 最後決定upgrade m5 作為hea影、旅行、後備機"},{"pid":"8973336c7d5647edada2e7d1a8d0dbcbdec556e4","tid":472642,"uid":8477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T02:31:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>路過想問下 <br />\nM6無左EVF <br />\n日頭會唔會好多時太光搞到睇唔到mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊後備機買M5定M6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真答你，買m5<br />\n貴小小有埋EVF <br />\n重小小，小到好難感覺到<br />\nTouch and drag<br />\n同埋m6 落左外置EVF 就冇得落閃<br />\n向下反mon 自拍果陣，望個mon = 望鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n我之前用緊m3, 最後決定upgrade m5 作為hea影、旅行、後備機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲想問多個問題<br />\n因為我有枝手動鏡加左ef電子adapter<br />\n如果到時m5加個ef mount先用枝鏡<br />\n個電子感應會唔會有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7101480f934dfee0b92cdd80f5583d0202eec31d","tid":472642,"uid":17166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:08:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早排買左EOS M6連EF-M 15-45mm f/3.5-6.3 IS STM<br />\n想換枝可以影人好啲既鏡頭 各位巴打有冇好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買定焦是常識吧</blockquote><br />\n去肥花入支2手sigma 17-50<br />\n影咩都得"},{"pid":"168793625850e3f5d67ba318d51b74c46b618773","tid":472642,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>路過想問下 <br />\nM6無左EVF <br />\n日頭會唔會好多時太光搞到睇唔到mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊後備機買M5定M6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真答你，買m5<br />\n貴小小有埋EVF <br />\n重小小，小到好難感覺到<br />\nTouch and drag<br />\n同埋m6 落左外置EVF 就冇得落閃<br />\n向下反mon 自拍果陣，望個mon = 望鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n我之前用緊m3, 最後決定upgrade m5 作為hea影、旅行、後備機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲想問多個問題<br />\n因為我有枝手動鏡加左ef電子adapter<br />\n如果到時m5加個ef mount先用枝鏡<br />\n個電子感應會唔會有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係唔係講手動鏡加canon EF to EF adapter? 你玩手動鏡都冇咩影響到你，peaking 都唔會受影響"},{"pid":"b3cfda895503bbf7ae8d2ba08ea8d3d83510be76","tid":472642,"uid":8477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>路過想問下 <br />\nM6無左EVF <br />\n日頭會唔會好多時太光搞到睇唔到mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊後備機買M5定M6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真答你，買m5<br />\n貴小小有埋EVF <br />\n重小小，小到好難感覺到<br />\nTouch and drag<br />\n同埋m6 落左外置EVF 就冇得落閃<br />\n向下反mon 自拍果陣，望個mon = 望鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n我之前用緊m3, 最後決定upgrade m5 作為hea影、旅行、後備機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲想問多個問題<br />\n因為我有枝手動鏡加左ef電子adapter<br />\n如果到時m5加個ef mount先用枝鏡<br />\n個電子感應會唔會有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係唔係講手動鏡加canon EF to EF adapter? 你玩手動鏡都冇咩影響到你，peaking 都唔會受影響</blockquote><br />\n明白 唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a974737074eca81fe3129918aa901646f09c3f3","tid":472642,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:51:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>路過想問下 <br />\nM6無左EVF <br />\n日頭會唔會好多時太光搞到睇唔到mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊後備機買M5定M6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會，但你可以裝evf同你反mon反到啱，btw你用開canon?"},{"pid":"408032c5997a6a8c3a777bc8585fd7c301b0aa97","tid":472642,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無EF mount adapter?<br />\n買支EF 50 F1.8 stm經adapter插落部機度</blockquote><br />\n就係諗緊買唔買得過 如果買左 之後EOS M出定焦就好似好傻仔</blockquote><br />\n咁諗先係傻仔，efm同ef影出嚟我覺得爭好遠，不過半底機用ef鏡會唔同啲，你自己睇文，我就鍾意2xmmef"},{"pid":"e71e9ba3d44cfe5daee3f85954350fc04049578b","tid":472642,"uid":13958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:40:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>路過想問下 <br />\nM6無左EVF <br />\n日頭會唔會好多時太光搞到睇唔到mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊後備機買M5定M6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真答你，買m5<br />\n貴小小有埋EVF <br />\n重小小，小到好難感覺到<br />\nTouch and drag<br />\n同埋m6 落左外置EVF 就冇得落閃<br />\n向下反mon 自拍果陣，望個mon = 望鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n我之前用緊m3, 最後決定upgrade m5 作為hea影、旅行、後備機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補多句，M6 落左evf 之後反mon 自拍係會擋住，完全係反人類設計。"},{"pid":"dc31944121527f5b6a193bb3bf8a9a105010a583","tid":472642,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>路過想問下 <br />\nM6無左EVF <br />\n日頭會唔會好多時太光搞到睇唔到mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊後備機買M5定M6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真答你，買m5<br />\n貴小小有埋EVF <br />\n重小小，小到好難感覺到<br />\nTouch and drag<br />\n同埋m6 落左外置EVF 就冇得落閃<br />\n向下反mon 自拍果陣，望個mon = 望鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n我之前用緊m3, 最後決定upgrade m5 作為hea影、旅行、後備機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補多句，M6 落左evf 之後反mon 自拍係會擋住，完全係反人類設計。</blockquote><br />\nM3 都係，仲有如果落mic 去hot shoe ，一樣反唔到mon"},{"pid":"3792dad048dd